{"tid":2266364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國抗爭　國會議員質詢到一半…亮15公分水果刀「自割手臂」","createTime":"2020-11-01T09:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T14:21:47.000Z","uid":261647,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a344515cea9b881fa139d2283225e7219dff0bda","tid":2266364,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=838600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D838600&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=6bd9dc6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D838600&h=7d2bb78a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=838600</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國學生近期發起民主抗議活動，反抗軍方對學校的影響，如今反抗議題已經全面擴大到連泰國根深蒂固的各種社會問題、貧富懸殊等狀況，都被涵蓋在其中；泰國反對黨一名議員27日更在國會上，抗議泰國總理帕拉育（Prayut Chan-ocha）無視學生的聲音，直接在現場捲起袖子、拿出預先準備好的小刀，猛然朝自己的手臂連劃2刀，嚇壞全場官員，更掀起國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日頭條》報導，泰國反對黨議員維薩恩&middot;泰塔希拉瓦特（Wisarn Techatheerawat）昨日在泰國國會上，發表了對此事學生抗議事件的看法，抨擊總理對抗議事件的無視，表示「我想不出解決這個問題的辦法，我不想看到孩子們流血」，自己願意身先士卒，直接在議會上拿出一把6英吋（約15.2公分）的長的小刀，往自己的手臂內側劃出兩道傷口，驚呆眾人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/28/2850562-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F2850562-PH.jpg&h=47f03cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲議員拿刀自己割傷手臂。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n維薩恩受傷後接著說，「我希望透過流血的方式，向總理表達我的決心」，他在動手之前也向總理喊話，要帕拉育想想他到底是想成為「英雄或暴君」，呼籲政府對進行全面改革。事後，相關人員也衝進會場替維薩恩包紮傷口，而反對黨則喊出要求總理請辭的口號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/23/1839831-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F23%2F1839831-PH.jpg&h=ad800f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰國總理帕拉育。（圖／翻攝自ประยุทธ์ จันทร์โอชา Prayut Chan-o-cha臉書）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，學生抗議的議題除了反對軍方影響校園以外，還對泰王拉瑪十世瓦吉拉隆功（King Vajiralongkorn）先前常駐德國一事感到不滿，德國外交部長馬斯（Heiko Maas）月初時就表示，德國政府不接受泰王在德國「遠端執政」，認為執政者應該返回自己的領土，示威者也對此事的合法性提出質疑，德國駐泰國大使館更成了抗議聚集地。"},{"pid":"d16fe8762bd2411844460db73de847815b8308d8","tid":2266364,"uid":226955,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZjY0Rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZjY0Rw.jpg&h=adb0ab84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd53bd9304bfe2c4f8fec2a8ae79a16899b6dd5a","tid":2266364,"uid":171506,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"香港無可能拎刀入立法會"},{"pid":"40749d46400fcb1535e36e28a23db620c6cc37fa","tid":2266364,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bb6db33bfdada34795a7593fbd4f5d53c6d814","tid":2266364,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16fe8762bd2411844460db73de847815b8308d8","tid":2266364,"uid":226955,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZjY0Rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZjY0Rw.jpg&h=adb0ab84&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"應該係Thailand先岩<br />\nThai=Indian=Hongkonger=Taiwanese"},{"pid":"62aedf10c9b5f9fca59cd5de8451aa4045638e60","tid":2266364,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"多隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394bf761a861e3f2d3c6e2305f5620879af6cc0a","tid":2266364,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"夠晒gimmick"},{"pid":"6d9ad632f41f2ff07b5395e9dcd7e91b44cda7ca","tid":2266364,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd53bd9304bfe2c4f8fec2a8ae79a16899b6dd5a","tid":2266